  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nNode has to use range sync to stay up to date instead of gossip block\r\n\r\n<img width=\"791\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-15 at 12 23 50\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/5b63e93e-b1fd-4684-8ae2-e102fd004744\">\r\n\r\nThis tells processed block are all from `beacon_blocks_by_range`\r\n<img width=\"805\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-15 at 12 24 21\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/bd93dcf5-dba5-438d-b935-6580942f856b\">\r\n\r\nThere is unknown block events, blocks are ~~downloaded~~ rarely downloaded ~~but never processed~~\r\n<img width=\"818\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-15 at 12 25 32\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/aa53c700-b41d-4131-b235-b85ee61baf3b\">\r\n\r\nGossip blocks are never received / processed at the period\r\n<img width=\"797\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-15 at 12 27 07\" src=\"https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/assets/10568965/2d7f8e10-d5d7-46ff-9e23-e72a32da565e\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNode should stay synced through gossip block\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Operating system\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\r\n\r\nv1.9.0-rc.2",
