    "body": "Unknown Block Sync really did not issue `beacon_blocks_by_root` much\r\n```\r\ngrep -e \"Added unknown block parent to pendingBlocks\" -rn beacon-2023-06-14.log | grep \"Jun-14 16:2\" |  wc -l\r\n48\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\ngrep -e \"Req  request sent method=beacon_blocks_by_root\" -rn beacon-2023-06-14.log | grep \"Jun-14 16:2\" |  wc -l\r\n3\r\n```\r\n\r\nnot sure if it's due to https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/5650, at least it'll add some more logs to debug if the issue ever happens again",
